
**a condition in which hair becomes brittle and breaks off**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   உரோமமுறிவு
-


**a condition of incomplete sleep in which some of the faculities are excited when the person becomes violent-sleep drungness somnolentia**
